		hem garment
		dye garment 32
		sell
		embroider garment "           a should be a two-argument curried function.\n"
		hem garment
		dye garment 32
		sell
		embroider garment "           For example, '5 10 x=>{ x } 0 a=>{ b=>{ a b ^ } } reduce' is equivalent to '0 10 9 8 7 6 5 ^ ^ ^ ^ ^ ^'.\n"
		hem garment
		dye garment 32
		sell
		embroider garment "A list of internal operators that shouldn't be used but can be:\n"
		hem garment
		dye garment 40
		sell
		embroider garment "   â˜ˆâ„Œ, 2: A Sieve of Erathostenes-y helper operator used in the definition of div. In short, it gets the number of divisors of the second argument, but the first argument serves as the 'starting value' in a way.\n"
		hem garment
		dye garment 30
		sell
		embroider garment "A list of other reserved symbols that I won't explain:\n"
		hem garment
		dye garment 40
		sell
		embroider garment "   ğ–©ğ”ğ”ğ’‚Õ–ğ–©‚ğ–©„ğ–©Â«Â»â²·ğ‹ªâ³š\n"
		hem garment
		dye garment 30
		sell
